  <h1>About</h1>

  <p>Alpha Factory Research is an independent quantitative research initiative.</p>

  <p>We develop and validate systematic trading hypotheses using a structured pipeline of data feasibility checks, frozen backtesting, forward evidence collection, and cost/concentration analysis.</p>

  <h2>We do NOT provide</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Trading signals</li>
    <li>Investment advice</li>
    <li>Portfolio management</li>
    <li>Financial consulting</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>We publish</h2>
  <p>Evidence-based research on systematic trading: mechanism discovery, validation methodologies, forward evidence results, and postmortem analysis of falsified hypotheses.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Email: <a href="mailto:support@yijigao.com">support@yijigao.com</a></p>
